---
const navLinks = [
  { href: '/tiemlennhadev/', label: 'Trang Chủ' },
  { href: '/tiemlennhadev/products', label: 'Sản Phẩm' },
  { href: '/tiemlennhadev/blog', label: 'Blog' },
  { href: '/tiemlennhadev/courses', label: 'Khóa Học' },
  { href: '/tiemlennhadev/charts', label: 'Thư Viện' },
];
---

<footer style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F9B2D7 0%, #CFECF3 50%, #DAF9DE 100%);">
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-16 py-10 md:py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-10">
      <!-- Column 1: Brand -->
      <div>
        <!-- Logo -->
        <a href="/tiemlennhadev/" class="flex flex-col leading-none mb-4">
          <span class="font-heading text-xl font-bold tracking-wide" style="color: #2C3E3F;">
            Tiệm Len
          </span>
          <span class="font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-0.5" style="color: #D4869E;">
            Nhà Dev
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="font-body text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed max-w-[320px]" style="color: #2C3E3F;">
          Handmade với tình yêu. Mỗi sản phẩm là một câu chuyện được đan từ từng sợi len.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2: Navigation -->
      <div>
        <span class="block text-[0.95rem] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-4" style="color: #D4869E;">Khám phá</span>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          {navLinks.map((link) => (
            <a
              href={link.href}
              class="font-body text-[1rem] transition-colors duration-base hover:translate-x-1 inline-block"
              style="color: #2C3E3F;"
            >
              {link.label}
            </a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3: Contact -->
      <div>
        <span class="block text-[0.95rem] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-4" style="color: #D4869E;">Kết nối</span>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          <a href="#" class="font-body text-[1rem] transition-colors duration-base hover:translate-x-1 inline-block" style="color: #2C3E3F;">Zalo</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-body text-[1rem] transition-colors duration-base hover:translate-x-1 inline-block" style="color: #2C3E3F;">Messenger</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-body text-[1rem] transition-colors duration-base hover:translate-x-1 inline-block" style="color: #2C3E3F;">Email</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar - Compact & Cute -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t flex flex-col items-center gap-2" style="border-color: rgba(212, 134, 158, 0.3);">
      <!-- Decorative Hearts -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <span style="color: #F9B2D7;">♥</span>
        <span style="color: #D4869E;">♥</span>
        <span style="color: #F9B2D7;">♥</span>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Handmade & Copyright -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap justify-center text-center">
        <span class="font-body text-[0.8rem]" style="color: #3D7A7F;">
          © 2026 Tiệm Len Nhà Dev
        </span>
        <span style="color: #D4869E;">•</span>
        <span class="font-body text-[0.8rem]" style="color: #3D7A7F;">
          Handmade with love in <span style="color: #DA251D;">Vietnam</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer a:hover {
    color: #D4869E !important;
  }
</style>
